race.comment: AKINA JACK (1) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only a nose from the winner Betty's Garden in second(28.83) at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Key chance in this line up. FEIKUAI CALVIN (6) goes very well this trip starting nine times for four wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (29.46) when second at Sandown in a Grade 4/5. Suited here and expected to run well. BANDIT BARBIE (2) showed strong early pace and stuck on well despite finishing out of the placings when fifth over 460m Warragul in 27.05. Should be thereabouts. ZIPPITY ZIPPIN' (7) won last start after racing on the pace. Right in the mix.
